Big Brother Naija star, Maria Chike Benjamin has apologized after mistaking Apostle Joshua Selman for the ‘Apostle’ she was accused of having an affair. The reality show star had earlier shared on Twitter. Realizing that she mistook him for someone else, Maria pleaded for forgiveness. She wrote; I stand corrected. My apologies to Apostle for getting names mixed up/wrong. Find it in your good heart to forgive my innocent tweet. Remain blessed